<HEADLINE>
<P>
PHOENIX AIRPORT LOGS 2 JET EMERGENCY LANDINGS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By United Press International 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>
<P>
PHOENIX 
</P>
</DATELINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Two commercial jets made emergency landings Sunday within minutes of each other 
at Phoenix Sky Harbor International Airport, one because of engine trouble and 
the other with three damaged tires, officials said. No injuries were reported. 
</P>
