200,000 Southlanders to the beach while firefighters grappled with brush fires. 
One 15-acre blaze near Sylmar, above, was blamed on spontaneous combustion in 
an 8-foot-deep compost heap. MIKE MEADOWS / Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
