on a 49-yard pass play in the first quarter at Anaheim. DON TORMEY / Los 
Angeles Times; Photo, COLOR, Rams Rout Cardinals (Orange County Edition) 
Michael Stewart made a 41-yard interception return for a touchdown as the Rams 
