<P>
Photo, Cardinal receiver Vai Sikahema is stopped after a reception, but the 
play was negated when a Phoenix player was called for holding. DON TORMEY / Los 
Angeles Times; Photo, (Orange County Edition) Vince Newsome tackles tight end 
Rob Awalt after two-yard reception. DON TORMEY / Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
